      "source": [
        "### Задание 1\n",
        "\n",
        "Метрикой качества в нашей задаче будет MAPE - Mean Absolute Percentage Error. Реализуйте её с заданным интефейсом и вычислите\n",
        "```MAPE(y_test, y_0)```, где ```y_0 = (mean(y_test), mean(y_test), ...)```"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 42,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "znoDavxyuLsi"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def MAPE(y_true, y_pred):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "        y_true: np.array (l)\n",
        "        y_pred: np.array (l)\n",
        "        ---\n",
        "        output: float [0, +inf)\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    y_true = np.asarray(y_true)\n",
        "    y_pred = np.asarray(y_pred)\n",
        "    \n",
        "    sum = 0\n",
        "    for i in range(len(y_true)):\n",
        "        if y_true[i] != 0:\n",
        "            mape = np.abs((y_true[i] - y_pred[i]) / y_true[i])\n",
        "            sum += mape\n",
        "    \n",
        "    ans = float(sum * 100 / len(y_true))\n",
        "    return ans"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "e6mTAykeojwp"
      },
      "outputs": [
